This paper is about software engineering and machine learning, specifically hyperparameter optimization for software effort estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses various machine learning algorithms and optimization techniques, which suggests that it could also fit into categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with data mining and analytics, which could place it in categories such as cs.SD (Software Development) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
